  &lt;p id="LMzy72"&gt;AI research company OpenAI is releasing a new machine learning tool that translates the English language into code. The &lt;a href="https://openai.com/blog/openai-codex/"&gt;software is called Codex&lt;/a&gt; and is designed to speed up the work of professional programmers, as well as help amateurs get started coding. &lt;/p&gt;
